    public class UpdateMessageProperties
extends AsyncDominoJNXJson

    UpdateMessageProperties iterates over lists of messages and sets / unsets three properties flags: follow up, soft delete, and unread.

      • process

        public void process(DbRequestParameters<io.vertx.core.json.JsonObject> request)
             throws java.lang.Exception

        process fetches lists of document ids. Tt then iterates over each list, fetches the proper document, and changes its corresponding message property.

        Parameters:
        followUpOn - document ids to turn on Follow Up
        followUpOFF - documents ids to turn off Follow Up
        softDeleteOn - documents ids to turn on Soft DeleteOn
        softDeleteOff - documents to turn off Soft Delete
        unreadOn - documents to turn on Unread
        unreadOff - documents to turn off Unread
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Anything that can go wrong, will go wrong
